refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
booleanevtgame_cgi_filepath stringfile_path
file_path is to be requested to execute, it should under a website directory.

&reftitle.parameters;


  file_path



    The absolute full path of the PHP file.

  &reftitle.examples;



    evtgame_cgi_filepath example


	<?php
	// /var/nginx/www/ is a website directory of nginx
	evtgame_cgi_filepath('/var/nginx/www/cgi.php');
	?>
